  <name>Nuvola Premium (WebApp Runtime)</name>
  <summary>Cloud music integration for your desktop</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Nuvola is a runtime for web-based music streaming services providing more native user experience and
      integration with Linux desktop environments than usual web browsers can offer. It tries to feel and look
      like a native application as possible. 
    </p>
  </description>
